Interface DataCenterInstancesReader<D extends DataCenterInstances>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileDataCenterInstancesReader, StandardInDataCenterInstancesReader

    public interface DataCenterInstancesReader<D extends DataCenterInstances>
    Describes a set of behaviors used for reading in data center capacity data. It is intended that each implementation of this interface provide a new strategy for how the data is stored and calculated while providing the best performance.

    Since:
    6/11/2013
    Author:
